[gd_scene load_steps=52 format=3]

; LAVA — Volcanic maze over a burning sea.
; Landmarks: Central Volcano (3 tiers + spiral), Lava Falls w/ secret
;   tunnel, Rock Arch, stepping-stone archipelago, sinking column route,
;   fire-plant gauntlet, dragon-egg vista, bomb pyramid, volcano core.
; Tiers: sea level plates / mid rock ring / summit caldera.
; Palette: basalt, lava, lava_crust, ember, stone_dark, red_rock,
;   bark (charred).
; Spawn: (0, 1, 24) basalt ledge facing the volcano.
; Content: 6 bobombs, 5 flame-plants, 2 charred goombas, 1 chuckya,
;   3 cuttlefish, ~30 yellow coins, 8 red coins, 2 stars (summit +
;   hidden core), 2 one-ups, 1 cap_metal.

